on of Bookmarks Dook\nThe plugin's GitHub site shows version 4.1.2\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/notepad-plus-plus/nppPluginList/commit/999d40437f3f3a8782ad2b08b9c34f4803479eaf"], "created_at": "2025-05-12T06:43:01Z"}
{"repo": "notepad-plus-plus/nppPluginList", "pull_number": 1064, "instance_id": "notepad-plus-plus__nppPluginList-1064", "issue_numbers": [1063], "base_commit": "b852b20153eeeeb79b2a9058139328455fc49e21", "patch": "diff --git a/src/pl.x64.json b/src/pl.x64.json\nindex 56c82695a..9cb5d1146 100644\n--- a/src/pl.x64.json\n+++ b/src/pl.x64.json\n@@ -1081,9 +1081,9 @@\n \t\t{\n \t\t\t\"folder-name\": \"NppMenuSearch\",\n \t\t\t\"display-name\": \"NppMenuSearch\",\n-\t\t\t\"version\": \"0.9.6\",\n-\t\t\t\"id\": \"7CA7BD5BB9D9FB6CB2CB54804F4BC7CC7C3E319D09ECBA761058C99E3ACC7870\",\n-\t\t\t\"repository\": \"https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.6/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.6_x64.zip\",\n+\t\t\t\"version\": \"0.9.7\",\n+\t\t\t\"id\": \"7da8e423a21382b0c58f9177439c1ce2ebc890754a7ea6708f05cceb240a8e11\",\n+\t\t\t\"repository\": \"https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.7_x64.zip\",\n \t\t\t\"description\": \"Adds a text field to the toolbar for searching menu items and preference dialog options.\",\n \t\t\t\"author\": \"Peter Frentrup\",\n \t\t\t\"homepage\": \"https://github.com/peter-frentrup/NppMenuSearch\"\ndiff --git a/src/pl.x86.json b/src/pl.x86.json\nindex e2e22bfb9..0a8a18c43 100644\n--- a/src/pl.x86.json\n+++ b/src/pl.x86.json\n@@ -1185,9 +1185,9 @@\n \t\t{\n \t\t\t\"folder-name\": \"NppMenuSearch\",\n \t\t\t\"display-name\": \"NppMenuSearch\",\n-\t\t\t\"version\": \"0.9.6\",\n-\t\t\t\"id\": \"7FC4D9DE6A117795C90AA36DC288C13D1E1B679A5F8AB642B0220A7F69E211E8\",\n-\t\t\t\"repository\": \"https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.6/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.6_x86.zip\",\n+\t\t\t\"version\": \"0.9.7\",\n+\t\t\t\"id\": \"644ffc369a2e88d495892dfd1c287ee66ce9be71c34b79d69ba327f6e3c99179\",\n+\t\t\t\"repository\": \"https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.7_x86.zip\",\n \t\t\t\"description\": \"Adds a text field to the toolbar for searching menu items and preference dialog options.\",\n \t\t\t\"author\": \"Peter Frentrup\",\n \t\t\t\"homepage\": \"https://github.com/peter-frentrup/NppMenuSearch\"\n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "NppMenuSearch to v0.9.7 (x64 / x86)\n### Summary\n\nPlugin Admin still offers **NppMenuSearch 0.9.6**, while **v0.9.7** has been published on GitHub and SourceForge since 2025-06-12.\n\n### Why update\n\n- **0.9.7** changes the default shortcut for \u201cMenu Search\u2026\u201d from **Ctrl+M** to **Ctrl+F1**, avoiding a clash with Notepad++\u2019s **Ctrl+M** (Mark). See [NppMenuSearch v0.9.7](https://github.com/peter-frentrup/NppMenuSearch/releases/tag/v0.9.7).\n- SourceForge hosts the official zips: [v0.9.7 folder](https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/).\n\n### Proposed change\n\n- Bump `version` to `0.9.7` in `src/pl.x64.json` and `src/pl.x86.json`.\n- Point `repository` to the v0.9.7 SourceForge URLs.\n- Update `id` (SHA-256 of each zip) accordingly.\n- Refresh `doc/plugin_list_x64.md` and `doc/plugin_list_x86.md` (or run `python validator.py all_md` after JSON edits).\n\n### Links\n\n- Release: [https://github.com/peter-frentrup/NppMenuSearch/releases/tag/v0.9.7](https://github.com/peter-frentrup/NppMenuSearch/releases/tag/v0.9.7)  \n- x64 zip: [https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.7_x64.zip](https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.7_x64.zip)  \n- x86 zip: [https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.7_x86.zip](https://sourceforge.net/projects/nppmenusearch/files/v0.9.7/NppMenuSearch_v0.9.7_x86.zip)\n\n### Reference\n\n- https://github.com/peter-frentrup/NppMenuSearch/issues/65\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/notepad-plus-plus/nppPluginList/commit/ea0baec416d6f273cfddbecdfd76c12d4f791e23"], "created_at": "2026-04-02T19:19:54Z"}
